{"tid":666853,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人口密集、租金又貴、交通發達，點解網上購物會咁落後？","createTime":"2018-05-16T08:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T08:58:26.000Z","uid":2023,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"9f610fb3fbcd9592b13f036037a44ee947e3ced9","tid":666853,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:51:37.000Z","msg":"明明發展網上購物嘅條件比起外國有過之而無不及，點解會落後日本、中國咁多？<br />\n人地網店仲平過實體店、全部免運費、一日內送到。<br />\n香港hktv mall日日蝕幾十萬。<br />\n<br />\n究竟係生活習慣問題？定其他原因？<br />\n<br />\nBtw我相信網店過多5年必然成為主流"},{"pid":"a52021741b14854465de4224b82ddef44d33ff53","tid":666853,"uid":5267,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afebbb54826f0e3cb452c81fa2c7f72a4be23330","tid":666853,"uid":2023,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a52021741b14854465de4224b82ddef44d33ff53","tid":666853,"uid":5267,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:55:05.000Z","msg":"咁日本點解成功？"},{"pid":"0401081a69efce028e34fd03aadeb656e73ce02e","tid":666853,"uid":172861,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c25353839454733d7725005e5dac4843056c1a","tid":666853,"uid":139322,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:55:31.000Z","msg":"有班好撚hea 既員工..<br />\n慢慢送貨 效率低<br />\n攪到運輸成本重皮<br />\n<br />\n(鳩up)"},{"pid":"aa8620d61bf2f9fc08b7a2814dd1ed1b24cab31e","tid":666853,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f0d7dc393396896deb69c5978172a913210bc78","tid":666853,"uid":10101,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:56:01.000Z","msg":"講到尾價錢<br />\nTaobao海外銷量數一數二"},{"pid":"3e791a71d03b33f1959f0ec422ded3fafd6aa520","tid":666853,"uid":13663,"like":0,"disl